reviews.review_description:
Similar gameplay to Tabor with a less serious vibe. It’s been fun exploring and collecting stuff however mission start and extraction could use some work;
I launched a mission and was stuck on a loading screen which required a reboot.  I launched a mission and the pod doors never opened after landing so I couldn’t leave the pod. I also approached a pod for extraction and it launched into orbit without me.

These things aside, I’ve been having a fun time and look forward to future updates!
